io.scanbot.sdk.ui.utils.navigator

Class NodeNavigator<A extends Activity>

  • ActivityBindingNavigator
    • io.scanbot.sdk.ui.utils.navigator.NodeNavigator<A>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Navigator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InternalBatchBarcodeCameraFragment.BarcodeCameraNavigator, InternalBarcodeCameraFragment.BarcodeCameraNavigator

    public class NodeNavigator<A extends Activity>
extends ActivityBindingNavigator

    Navigator which navigates between interface NodeNavigator.NavigationNode.

    You must call .bind before using the navigator and .unbind when bound Activity is about to be paused.

    When navigator is being bound to again, it replays the last navigation node.

    When navigator is about to be unbound - it calls NavigationNode.navigateFrom so you will have the chance to dispose resources associated with the node.

    See Also:
    interface NodeNavigator.NavigationNode, .bind, .unbind, Activity, NavigationNode.navigateFrom
